## Project Context

- **Client:** Gerotech — Michigan CNC machinery distributor, Haas Factory Outlet, est. 1987
- **Agency:** CloudMellow (Matt)
- **This repo:** Static HTML/CSS/JS prototype (NOT the production build — final site will be WordPress)

---

## Tech Stack

- Pure HTML5 / CSS3 (custom properties) / vanilla JS (ES6) — zero frameworks
- Fonts: Navigo (Adobe Fonts, kit `lqh7ybe`) — 400 + 700 weights only
- CSS load order: `assets/css/tokens.css` → `assets/css/components.css` → `assets/css/layout.css`
- JS: `nav.js` (both pages), `slider.js` (homepage only), `filter.js` (ES page only), `animations.js` (both), `testimonials.js` (homepage)

## Typography System (2026-07-14 review)

- **The Adobe Fonts kit (lqh7ybe) serves Navigo 400 + 700 ONLY** (plus italics). Weights 500/600/800 silently fall back — never use them. All `--fw-*` tokens now map to the two real faces. If Matt adds weights to the kit, update tokens.css.
- Type scale lives in tokens.css: `--fs-hero/display/h1/h2/h3` (fluid clamps — do NOT re-override sizes in media queries) + `--fs-lede/body/ui/caption`. Tracking: `--ls-hero…h3` (negative, tightens with size), `--ls-caps` 0.14em (eyebrows), `--ls-meta` 0.08em (card labels). Leading: `--lh-*`.
- All headlines use scale tokens + `text-wrap: balance`; body/quotes use `--lh-body` and `text-wrap: pretty`; intro body capped at 62ch measure.
- Buttons: `text-transform: uppercase` + 0.05em letter-spacing, `--fw-bold` (maps to Navigo 700)

## Key Brand Tokens
- Orange: `#F38A2C` (`--clr-orange`)
- Dark bg: `#1C1C21` (`--clr-dark-bg`)
- Dark nav/footer: `#3A3A40` (`--clr-dark-nav`)
- Body gray: `#6B6B76` (`--clr-gray-body`)
- Border: `#E4E4EA` (`--clr-gray-border`)
- Max-width: 1200px (homepage) / 1120px (ES page)
- Radii: buttons 8px, cards 0 (squared), pills 99px

